        "subject": "LU-9011 component: to delete file ending with :rhel5.ed",
        "message": "LU-9011 component: to delete file ending with :rhel5.ed\n\ncontrib/patches/ofed/\n01-dont-include-openib-initscript:rhel5.ed\nWe probably don't need this\n\"contrib/patches/ofed/\n01-dont-include-openib-initscript:rhel5.ed\" file\nin our tree  since RHEL5 support is very outdated.\nIf this file is required, then it is better to rename it as\n\"contrib/patches/ofed/\n01-dont-include-openib-initscript-rhel5.ed\"\nso that on Windows it can be cloned properly.\n\nSigned-off-by: dilip krishnagiri <dilipx.krishnagiri@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I5b4b0440e3b76ced9aebe329ece32719ad24fd23\n"
      },
